# Windtunnel — the repo is PUBLIC and world-readable. No secrets, ever
# (CLAUDE.md §4, §6). This file keeps env files and build cruft out; it is a
# backstop, not the control — secrets live only in Render env vars / Actions
# secrets, never in a committed file or a run directory.

# Secrets / env
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
!config/*.yml

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
.uv/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# Node / frontend
node_modules/
frontend/dist/
frontend/.vite/
*.local

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/

# Notes:
# - runs/ IS committed (it is the durable store, TECH_SPEC §4). Do not ignore it.
# - kb/*.sqlite ARE committed unless too large (then release-asset pointers,
#   TECH_SPEC §2). Do not add a blanket *.sqlite ignore here.
